name: Inferno Maw Icebox
text: In the dusky kitchen of Sorcerer Hale, the Icebox grumbled—fiery cracks lined its frame. Each time Hale injected his creations with frosty magic, the Icebox roared, famished, its inner void insatiable. One perilous eve, the Icebox yawned wide, and with a fiery belch, it devoured the leftover dragon stew.
